{"tid":2337690,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"扶貧委員會：五個香港人有一人貧窮","createTime":"2020-12-23T12:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T12:52:10.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"74dca096472b6e8623fefd3a851f3b581f74ad75","tid":2337690,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:46:00.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】扶貧委員會開會，討論2019年香港的貧窮狀況，去年的貧窮人口達149萬，創11年來的新高。<br />\n<br />\n本港貧窮人口創下自2009年以來新高，去年政策介入前的貧窮人口達149.1萬，比前年增加了約9萬人，貧窮率是21.4%，即大約五個香港人中，便有一人貧窮，是11年以來最高。<br />\n<br />\n如果計及綜援、生果金及長者生活津貼等恆常現金政策介入後，貧窮人口為109.8萬，貧窮率為15.8%。<br />\n<br />\n按住戶人數劃分的相對貧窮線，一人家庭月入少於4500元便算貧窮，標準比前年提高了500元，二人家庭維持在一萬元，三至六人家庭的標準均有輕微上升。<br />\n<br />\n唐女士一家三口主要倚靠現時做散工廚師的丈夫來維持生計，月入約1萬2千元，算是活在貧窮線下，她們沒有申請綜援。<br />\n<br />\n唐女士認為，比起現金支援，她更希望政府能增撥資源，增加託管服務，讓她也可以做兼職幫補家計。<br />\n<br />\n唐女士：「先生失業時很害怕，不知何時才找到工作，生活怎麼辦？小朋友太小了，不放心她一人在家，始終要人照顧或有人陪做功課，有託管服務是最好的。」<br />\n<br />\n她又表示，疫情下停課亦影響了小朋友的學習進度，期望政府能加強對基層小朋友的學習支援。"},{"pid":"fc0927df909413dee12a9b3d5ae18829f2e5493e","tid":2337690,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:46:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=417705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417705&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=453ccfd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417705&h=db7194b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=417705</a>"},{"pid":"b6ff01083d7270baff50b04ee6cb80538bb443e7","tid":2337690,"uid":375148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:47:25.000Z","msg":"成日話香港人窮 但係唔知我離地高定 身邊啲人窮極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係iPhone就日日食得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44ea2a73ee37684e871e448631c9add44b78aa4","tid":2337690,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:47:32.000Z","msg":"衰過中國 中國已經全面脫貧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36caa8b551023244c7e3752284799a8b5d4c1b54","tid":2337690,"uid":39777,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c44ea2a73ee37684e871e448631c9add44b78aa4","tid":2337690,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:47:32.000Z","msg":"衰過中國 中國已經全面脫貧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:50:41.000Z","msg":"等等先，咁香港唔計中國架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829bddeed58a81ea8da117f46ed2073b77b4da2f","tid":2337690,"uid":197920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:52:10.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;一人家庭月入少於4500元便算貧窮&rdquo;<br />\n$4500住籠屋都租唔起啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}